{"tid":2341260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Fb 新歷史Page《時空筆記》係紅色媒體，立即Unfollow!","createTime":"2020-12-26T08:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T20:00:17.000Z","uid":90305,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"01e59cc34d749bed80fbbc68211df169a8c2d8ea","tid":2341260,"uid":90305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"鍾意睇歷史，尤其香港歷史嘅，<br />\n都會被Facebook 派<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins><ins><span class=\"x-large\">《時空筆記》</span></ins></ins></span></strong>廣告。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">唔好俾佢五光十色嘅香港歷史圖片吸引</span></span></strong>，佢肯定係紅色媒體page！<br />\n<strong>證據擺最底</strong>，講咗點解共產黨要搞歷史Page先：<br />\n1. 當然係要搶佔「歷史」話語權，用佢說法講歷史，甚至歪曲事實，隱共產黨之惡，揚中國之善。<br />\n2. 舊年運動，佢地發現好多<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"teal\">接觸銀髮族</span></span>嘅page，好多都係黃。<br />\n3. 佢地並唔係意識唔到，2014年前，梁振英體系已經搞過「史檔」page，呃到好多人（包括我），但一到雨傘即刻現晒形，維穩、避開所有社會事不談，人地問佢點睇就顧左右而言他，結果變咗廢page，就終極現形。<br />\n4. 中共今年係香港「做歷史」做到出晒面：教育- DSE歷史題事件；新聞- 重寫721、理大、612；Wiki 戰。Social Media 當然係進攻點。<br />\n5. 中國人自古就有「正統」，「修正史」觀念，即係新政權繼承上一個政權，對歷史就應該有終極話語權。其他人講嘅都係只供參考，不可信。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">證據</span></span>：<br />\n1. <strong>李光耀都話社會主義中國最好</strong><br />\n《時空筆記》有好多香港歷史，五光十色，目不暇給。就咁睇以為好本土，Click 入去就會見到大量Post <span class=\"green\">宣傳中國同社會主義優越性</span>。11月就用李光耀去執行任務：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gB59h9U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgB59h9U.png&h=9e2b46ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李光耀講大國勃起<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3EFpQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3EFpQ0.png&h=350b6626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李光耀為習近平打飛機 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suuFpRD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuuFpRD.png&h=9cd8e0f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李光耀話中國不適合民主<br />\n仲有 李光耀係英國教育，但玩中國棋、李光耀係中國人後代、李光耀傾向社會主義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102348188160887/photos/pcb.199870921741946/199870771741961/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102348188160887%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.199870921741946%2F199870771741961%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=e4ff6671\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102348188160887/photos/pcb.199870921741946/199870771741961/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>雙十一</strong><br />\n呢個唔洗解釋啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90xWHFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90xWHFn.png&h=bc9d5ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>深圳經濟特區是最勁</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsqAYeg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsqAYeg.png&h=65a3012f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.<strong>中國女排 嫦娥五號 中國人在南極</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHX0pU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHX0pU9.png&h=061c499c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.<strong>Related Page 團結香港基金</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xJOyPt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xJOyPt.png&h=5430dedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n仲有好多，自己慢慢睇。大家小心軟性共媒，佢地其實唔係防不勝防，只要見到新page有人share/ sponsor，入去page睇吓先，就唔難發現！"},{"pid":"fb69007b616eec029d65c068362256cd5361b8ac","tid":2341260,"uid":126412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08865476d78afdd4ab1f62290609ba6d4bb713d5","tid":2341260,"uid":90305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdec0987905dc567816eb92ec3f1a96eb10ad5f8","tid":2341260,"uid":164646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0de285cbf84a603da536a4c5203e5c73e969c252","tid":2341260,"uid":90305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20